Subject: CHANGE: add a check for your model before Markovian analysis
Date: Thu, 10 Jun 2010 15:57:24 -0600
X-Mailer: Apple Mail (2.936)

Before doing Markov analysis, check if the LPN can be analyzed.

All transitions must have an exponential delay (or possibly 0 delay,  
but support is needed for immediate transitions).

All assignments should not include random functions.

No continuous variables.


